import React, { Component } from 'react' import _ from 'lodash' import { getCampaignListAction } from '@/actions/CreateCampaign/manageCampaign' import { Icon, Menu, Table, Progress } from 'semantic-ui-react' class TableExamplePagination extends Component { state = { activePage: 1, } componentWillUpdate() { getCampaignListAction(this.state.activePage) } setPage = activePage => { this.setState({ activePage }) } render() { const { headers } = this.props const { data } = this.props.CampaignList if (data) { return null } const { activePage } = this.state return (
{headers && ( {headers.map(header => ( {header.value} ))} )} {campaigns && campaigns.map((part, index) => ( {index + 1} {_.capitalize(part.name)} {_.capitalize(part.campaignType)} {_.capitalize(part.status)} {_.capitalize(part.channel)} Impression : 70 Click : 70 Bounce : 70 Browse: 70 Action ))} 1 {/* 2 3 4 */}
) } } export default TableExamplePagination
